            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the beef has browned, add the<strong> chopped garlic</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) to the pan and cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p><p>Add your <strong>honey</strong> and <strong>half</strong> your <strong>soy sauce</strong> (save the rest for later!) and cook for 4-5 min or until the beef becomes crispy, sticky and cooked through (no pink meat!) – this is your <strong>crispy chilli beef</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1614080988285-x200.jpg",
