            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the beef is cooking, dissolve your <strong>beef stock mix</strong>, <strong>sriracha</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) and <strong>remaining soy sauce </strong>in<strong> </strong>600ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[800ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[1L] </span><strong>boiled water </strong>– this is your<strong> spicy stock</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
