    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large pot over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>halved</strong> <strong>pak choi</strong> and <strong>spicy</strong> <strong>stock</strong> and cook for 2-3 min until the pak choi has started to soften</p><p>Stir through your <strong>udon noodles</strong> and cook for 1 min further – this is your <strong>udon broth</strong></p><p>Tip: You may need to gently break apart the noodles with a fork!</p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
