    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the<strong> udon broth</strong> topped with the <strong>crispy chilli beef</strong>, <strong>carrot ribbons </strong>and <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Sprinkle over your <strong>toasted</strong> <strong>sesame seeds </strong>and <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
